Invocation Name: bandar mama
des:
"Bandar Mama Pehen Pyjama" is a Hindi Rhyme funny song. Enjoy Kids.

We have updated the skill with a more smooth and fault-free experience. We are continuing the legacy of the previous skill with a more advanced and smooth voice experience.


bandar mama will take you on an adventurous ride to the jungle. Whether it is time to sleep or dinner, play this rhyme for kids and your kid will love it.


Once invoked, Alexa will automatically start the conversation and play the audio. Sit back, relax, and enjoy the rhyme of bandar mama. To start again on finishing one story, you can ask Alexa to open it again.
